{"tid":430149,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【消失20年】麥記重推$39萬「四川辣醬」 美食客搶唔到打大交","createTime":"2017-10-09T14:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T14:56:38.000Z","uid":47272,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2487b889111a9280a6a7b851db6d9793e69c4fcd","tid":430149,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:14:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171009&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57309420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171009%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57309420&d=1sL3qW5UPY4I6ATSgvDB5dWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=d1898460\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171009%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57309420&h=b65f3f14\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171009&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57309420</a><br />\n食炸雞，你愛點哪種醬？在美國，有一款麥當勞在1998年短暫推出的四川辣醬（Szechuan sauce），被奉為傳世經典。消失了將近20年，近日卻因為一套動畫《Rick And Morty》再次被熱炒。早前單單一張四川辣醬的照片，在Ebay上被炒到5萬多美元（約39萬港元），更有上萬網友湧入請願網站，要求麥當勞重新推出這隻辣醬。上周六，麥當勞宣佈在指定分店限量推出四川醬，但因供不應求，引起排隊的美國市民不滿，在餐廳內叫口號「We want Sauce」（我們要辣醬），更有顧客大打出手，要報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n失望的粉絲為爭奪辣醬大打出手，甚至打電話報了警。有顧客高舉標語，高呼「我們要辣醬」。搶到辣醬的消費者，甚至在拍賣網上以數百美元叫賣。該快餐公司隨後發佈聲明道歉，稱並未意識到辣醬會如此受歡迎，又承諾今年冬天會再次推出並大量供應。"},{"pid":"1a59b928e296d6d0af15175c44a6acaae644cffa","tid":430149,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:15:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4524d8f27fa40e79c72099077ee235d9b7a48030","tid":430149,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:15:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171009&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57309420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171009%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57309420&d=1sL3qW5UPY4I6ATSgvDB5dWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=d1898460\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%